title: Andy Warstar & Friends - 10/20/02 Portland, OR
description:
Warstars live at Music Millenium up on NW 23rd street. This was an afternoon gig,

playing to a bunch of zombie shoppers. A few teenage girls remarked that they

understood what the band was "trying to do". Warstars never tried. They just did.

Free CDs up the yang were given out for free, as usual. The record store guy cut

the band off early, citing the volume being a problem. Are ALL people stupid and

lame? No. Just asshole kids who work at record stores who listen to Oasis.


google andy warstar - visit www.andywarstar.com - for the warheads!
